    "notes": [
      "Standard Move Maneuver (1-4AP, or more)\nGM determined, can be rushed",
      "Hasted 8APAdrenal Speed Absolute Success\nSpeed IV\nHaste IV",
      "Concentration requries no AP, but doubles AP cost of all additional actions and halves movement.\n\nDouble concentration requires Mental Focus roll every round, or both concentrations are failed (only 50% creep move possible, requiring MM roll)\n\nInstantaneous (0AP) actions are free, but only one is allowed per turn. Further instant actions cost 1AP (or 2 if concentrating).\n\nMultiple Spells can be cast in a single round, but each additional spell has a cumulative -50 penalty to casting (in addition to any rushing penalties). Physical multi-attacks to not suffer this penalty.",
      "Actions can flow over into the following round if incomplete in the round they were started.\n\nUpkeep (stun, bleed, stagger, etc.) occurs at the end of the round."
    ]
  },
